                                The basic line distinguishing cryptomoney from the real is the way of their emergence in digital space. So, real means of payment are required to be deposited into a certain account or an e-wallet in the beginning, and cryptomonetary units appear in electronic form initially. "Release" of digital money happens in various ways: ICO (primary placement of coins, system of investment), mining (maintenance of the special platform for creation of new cryptomoney), forzhing (formation of new blocks in already available cryptocurrencies). That is the cryptocurrency arises directly from the Internet.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
