                        </div>
                        <div class="info">
                            <p class="desc">
                                Other important difference from usual currency consists in release decentralization. The release of electronic currency represents generation of a mathematical code with the subsequent digital signature. The Central Bank has right to issue only real money. But crypto money can release any person. To make operations by means of cryptocurrency, it isn't necessary to contact with any third-party organizations (banks).
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="swiper-slide">
