                        </div>
                        <div class="info">
                            <p class="desc">
                                Payments by means of digital money are made exactly as well as usual wire transfers on the system of non-cash payment. The exception is the Exchange, through which cryptomanias can be monetized, that is, switch to the usual methods of payment. The address of such currency happens on the blockchain system. This system represents the database distributed millions of personal computers around the world. At the same time storage and data recording at the address of cryptomoney happens on all devices at once that guarantees absolute transparency and openness of the made transactions.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="swiper-slide">
                        <div class="img">
                            <img src="~/Content/img/crypto5.jpeg" alt="">
                        </div>
                        <div class="info">
                            <p class="desc">
                                The popularity of cryptocurrency is caused by requirements of time. In a century of universal distribution of information technologies universal means of payment which it would be possible to pay off in electronic space without binding to a certain country or establishment are extremely demanded. The cryptocurrency became such means. For payments with virtual money only their number therefore the cryptocurrency doesn't need in real terms is used. Digital means of payment are protected by a cryptographic code that does them by more reliable in comparison with real money. And owing to absolute decentralization of issue of virtual coins, they can't be forged and forbidden.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="swiper-slide">
                        <div class="img">
